## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [dot2-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;dot2-1 mutants are dwarved plants that display an aberrant spurred leaf venation pattern and fail to flower. They also have an abnormal cotyledon number, shorter petioles, significantly shorter roots and smaller rosettes when compared to wild-type plants.
